TextEng: Who are you?
Is this an ambush? I'll not trust you.
Relax! I work for no one. Just tell me who you are.
Text: 진정하세요! 저는 아무 편도 아닙니다. 누구신지만 말해주세요.

TextEng: Who you is, eh?
Me not likes trick. You move slow!
Me says stop yammering! Me wanting know name.
Text: 나 떠드는 거 그만하라고! 나 이름 알고 싶어.

TextEng: How do I know you're actually a prisoner, that this isn't some ruse?
Text: 당신이 정말 죄수인지 어떻게 알죠? 이게 속임수 아니고요?

TextEng: You tell me some stuff, and maybe I'll let you go.
Can you make it worth my while to free you?
Text: 날 풀어주면 뭔가 대가를 줄 수 있나요?

TextEng: How me know you not trying trick me?
Text: 너 속임수 안 쓰는 거 어떻게 알아?

TextEng: Me gots questions. You answer, maybe me let go?
Text: 나 질문 있어. 너 대답하면 풀어줄까?

TextEng: Me gets reward for freeing you?
I don't buy that. I'm killing you.
Me not born yesterday. Me born long before! And you die now.
Text: 나 어제 태어난 거 아니야. 나 오래전에 태어났어! 그리고 너 지금 죽어.

TextEng: Fine. Tell me something.
You're worthless. Go away.
Me gets stuff told to? Okay. Is good.
Me says go away. Me not wants you here. Go!
Text: 나 가라고 했어. 나 너 여기 있는 거 싫어. 가!

TextEng: Why are you a prisoner here? What's this war about?
Text: 왜 여기 갇혀 있죠? 이 전쟁은 뭐죠?

TextEng: Can you tell me anything about these caves?
Text: 이 동굴에 대해 뭔가 말해줄 수 있나요?

TextEng: What can you tell me of the orcs and goblins?
Text: 오크와 고블린에 대해 뭘 알려줄 수 있나요?

TextEng: That's enough questions. You can go.
How you gets in prison?
You tells stuff about prison? To me?
What you tells of orcs and goblins?
Me not got more questions. Me got message for you leaving. Go bye!
Text: 나 더 질문 없어. 나 너한테 가라는 말 있어. 가 안녕!

TextEng: I don't understand what you mean by making strength.
Text: 힘을 만든다는 게 무슨 뜻인지 이해가 안 되는군요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Who's the master?
Do they have leaders to their tribes?
What means you making strength? You get big, strong group?
Text: 힘 만든다는 거 무슨 뜻이야? 크고 강한 무리 만들어?

TextEng: Orcs and goblins got leaders in caves?
Army? What do you mean?
Army? What means you army?
I'll kill you now, monster!
Me kill you!
